<div class="solution-begin"><button id='sol-start-4' class="jk-circle-right solution-icon clickable" onclick="toggle_visibility('sol-body-4', 'sol-start-4')">  Solution </button></div><div class="solution-body" id = "sol-body-4" style="display: none;">






::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
trolley <- read_csv("https://uoepsy.github.io/data/msmr_trolley.csv")
head(trolley)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
# A tibble: 6 × 4
  PID   frame    lives   lever
  <chr> <chr>    <chr>   <dbl>
1 PPT_1 positive 5lives      1
2 PPT_1 positive 15lives     1
3 PPT_1 positive 5lives      1
4 PPT_1 positive 15lives     1
