```{.r .cell-code}
trolley |>
  group_by(PID) |>
  summarise(
    n_trials = n(),
    n_frame = n_distinct(frame),
    n_lives = n_distinct(lives),
    n_combn = n_distinct(frame,lives)
  ) |>
  summary()
```

